    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the memories aren't the problem, it's the emptiness. i wake up and i realize i have to do this all over again... the eating, the working, the sleeping alone. it feels so pointless. like i'm just dragging this heavy thing around for no reason. i just want the weight to stop. i just want it to be quiet for good.",
