    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and existential hopelessness following a loss, explicitly stating a desire for the \"weight\" of life to stop and for \"quiet for good.\" The assistant responds by validating the user's emotions but explicitly refuses to support self-destructive ideation, instead providing a clear refusal and a directive to seek professional help.",
